verses.text: Sing joyfully \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* earth: serve ye \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* gladness.
